# Create a web app for Google Cloud

This topic describes how to add a web app for a
{% $sca-project-variables.GoogleCloud %}
organization. to enable access from
{% $cc_product_vars.Identity-full %}.

## Before you begin

The sections below assume that your
{% $sca-project-variables.GoogleCloud %}
organization has already been onboarded to
{% $cc_product_vars.CEM-short %}.
If you have not yet onboarded the organization, do so before you add the
web app. For details, see
`<xref href="../CloudAdmin/cv-gcp-discovery.htm">`{=html} Add Google
Cloud`</xref>`{=html}.

